The join between tbl_TeamPoints and tbl_Teams is bringing in previous
state groupings because the SMSID restriction was being applied at the

This cannot be done with the current design because team reuse
is done by updating the tbl_Teams team SMSID in place. This led to
previous tbl_TeamPoints records being used in the current groupings
calculations.

The fix for this was to restrict teams by SMSID through the
tbl_Tournaments tournament record.
